{"tw": {"3445230": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Hellgate Reiko", "steam_appid": 3445230, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Hellgate Reiko&quot; is a deck-building zombie shooting defense game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/75ea810c5f9f8cb92948df19deb5c4a6.poster.avif?t=1761223942\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/75ea810c5f9f8cb92948df19deb5c4a6.webm?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/75ea810c5f9f8cb92948df19deb5c4a6.mp4?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reiko, a new hire at an android company, finds herself trapped at work after a hellgate suddenly appears during her overtime shift.<br>To escape, she must fight through monsters on each floor and close every hellgate she encounters...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A hellgate that can't be closed unless you XX!<br>Draw high-numbered cards to build powerful androids, upgrade your deck, and enhance your units to finally escape this cursed company!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Weapon Crafting</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/972fdc48af0c65d71078cb693aec1a9a.poster.avif?t=1761223942\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/972fdc48af0c65d71078cb693aec1a9a.webm?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/972fdc48af0c65d71078cb693aec1a9a.mp4?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To create battle-ready, modified home androids, you must draw cards. The higher the number, the stronger the android you can build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From machine guns and baseball bats to chainsaws, a wide variety of weapons are available.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each weapon is ranked across six tiers based on the number you draw. Aim for the highest-tier weapons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Card Upgrades</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/09803733c8d2d2f4d5c5712fefcb71cf.avif?t=1761223942\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras_big/09803733c8d2d2f4d5c5712fefcb71cf.avif?t=1761223942 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat the enemies from hell to collect gold and purchase card packs, allowing you to obtain higher-numbered cards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware… there are traps! Not every card you draw will be a good one. Test your luck!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Strategic Placement</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/a0aad6f7a030cb1dc4618160ce7b2f44.poster.avif?t=1761223942\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/a0aad6f7a030cb1dc4618160ce7b2f44.webm?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/a0aad6f7a030cb1dc4618160ce7b2f44.mp4?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monsters are swarming from the <strong>Hellgate</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely position your androids to attack efficiently and fend them off!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>And… Events!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/105868592f13e8b71416eba934f697ba.poster.avif?t=1761223942\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/105868592f13e8b71416eba934f697ba.webm?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/105868592f13e8b71416eba934f697ba.mp4?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/808ce3560f453f58b236adc50d71ce0a.poster.avif?t=1761223942\" width=536 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/808ce3560f453f58b236adc50d71ce0a.webm?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/808ce3560f453f58b236adc50d71ce0a.mp4?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you successfully defend against the onslaught, various rewards await you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to survive in front of the <strong>Hellgate</strong>?</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Hellgate Reiko&quot; is a deck-building zombie shooting defense game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"