span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reiko, a new hire at an android company, finds herself trapped at work after a hellgate suddenly appears during her overtime shift.<br>To escape, she must fight through monsters on each floor and close every hellgate she encounters...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A hellgate that can't be closed unless you XX!<br>Draw high-numbered cards to build powerful androids, upgrade your deck, and enhance your units to finally escape this cursed company!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Weapon Crafting</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/972fdc48af0c65d71078cb693aec1a9a.poster.avif?t=1761223942\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/972fdc48af0c65d71078cb693aec1a9a.webm?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/972fdc48af0c65d71078cb693aec1a9a.mp4?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To create battle-ready, modified home androids, you must draw cards. The higher the number, the stronger the android you can build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From machine guns and baseball bats to chainsaws, a wide variety of weapons are available.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each weapon is ranked across six tiers based on the number you draw. Aim for the highest-tier weapons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Card Upgrades</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/09803733c8d2d2f4d5c5712fefcb71cf.avif?t=1761223942\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras_big/09803733c8d2d2f4d5c5712fefcb71cf.avif?t=1761223942 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat the enemies from hell to collect gold and purchase card packs, allowing you to obtain higher-numbered cards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware… there are traps! Not every card you draw will be a good one. Test your luck!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Strategic Placement</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/a0aad6f7a030cb1dc4618160ce7b2f44.poster.avif?t=1761223942\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/a0aad6f7a030cb1dc4618160ce7b2f44.webm?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/a0aad6f7a030cb1dc4618160ce7b2f44.mp4?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monsters are swarming from the <strong>Hellgate</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely position your androids to attack efficiently and fend them off!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>And… Events!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/105868592f13e8b71416eba934f697ba.poster.avif?t=1761223942\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/105868592f13e8b71416eba934f697ba.webm?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/105868592f13e8b71416eba934f697ba.mp4?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/808ce3560f453f58b236adc50d71ce0a.poster.avif?t=1761223942\" width=536 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/808ce3560f453f58b236adc50d71ce0a.webm?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/extras/808ce3560f453f58b236adc50d71ce0a.mp4?t=1761223942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you successfully defend against the onslaught, various rewards await you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to survive in front of the <strong>Hellgate</strong>?</p>", "short_description": "Reiko, a new hire at an android company, finds herself unable to leave work due to the sudden appearance of hellgates. Upgrade your cards and enhance your androids to deal with the hellgates that can't be closed unless you XX — and escape this cursed company!", "supported_languages": "English, Japanese, Korean", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/header.jpg?t=1761223942", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/a1495c6212add9652ec32b8c3c3f4b8e3793b40d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1761223942", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445230/a1495c6212add9652ec32b8c3c3f4b8e3793b40d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1761223942", "website": "https://ci-en.dlsite.com/creator/30987", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10 or later<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Processor with SSE2 instruction set support (x86, x64 architecture)<br></li><li><strong>Mem